Teamodoro is intended to be a team-based pomodoro system.

Main features include:
  * Team dashboard
  * Multiple pomodoros running concurrently
  * Goal setting per pomodoro ("what will we achieve in this pom?")
  * Show current/last goal being worked on (replace 00:00 time?)
  * Leave a message for someone in a pomodoro without interrupting them
  * Gravatar support

  
 